<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kohl Supports Call For Public Sector Pay Freeze </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1901131394 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1240 GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1901131394 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DDP/ADN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Magdeburg (DDP/ADN) -- Chancellor Helmut Kohl has 
supported the call by Interior Minister Manfred Kanther for a 
pay freeze in the public sector. It is impossible to move 
outside the general development of the economy, the chancellor 
said at a news conference in Magdeburg today. Kohl declined to 
give figures for his expectations for the pay and conditions 
round. Securing jobs has priority, he said. 

</TEXT>

