<F P=103> LD1901173394 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DDP/ADN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Leipzig (ADN) -- Verbundnetz Gas AG (VNG), Leipzig, 
and Wintershall Erdgas Handelshaus GmbH (WIEH), Berlin, have 
reached a compromise one day before Russian natural gas 
deliveries were due to stop. The two companies announced in a 
joint statement this evening that an agreement on price was 
reached "at the last minute." The parties willl sign a 
long-term supply contract for Russian gas before the end of the 
month. 

