<F P=100> GREECE </F>
<H3> <TI>   First Greek Soldiers Return From Somalia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2201161394 Athens ELEVTHEROTIPIA in Greek 22 Jan 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> NC2201161394 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens ELEVTHEROTIPIA </F>


<TEXT>
