<H3> <TI>   Cabinet To Decide on Transrapid Train by March </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2101165394 Berlin DIE WELT in German 21 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> AU2101165394 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DIE WELT </F>


