<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Manfred Brunner Forms New Party </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2301192194 Mainz ZDF Television Network in German 1800 GMT 
23 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2301192194 </F>
<F P=104>  Mainz ZDF Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Federation of Free Citizens is the name of a new 
party founded in Wiesbaden today by former Bavarian Free 
Democratic Party of Germany Chairman Manfred Brunner. The 
objectives of the European critic are less European centralism, 
no joint currency, and a market economy-oriented policy. 

</TEXT>

