<H3> <TI>   Italian Republican Party Reelects La Malfa </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2201165194 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1540 GMT 
22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2201165194 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Italian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Italian Republican Party's [PRI] National 
Council has reelected Giorgio la Malfa as political secretary. 
  La Malfa received 72 votes for and nine against [his 
reappointment]. There were 14 abstentions and nine blank 
ballots. La Malfa resigned as PRI secetary 11 months ago [when 
he was involved in the Clean Hands investigation]. 

</TEXT>

