<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] Israeli President Ezer Weizman has arrived in 
Ankara as the official guest of President Suleyman Demirel. 
