Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Bonn (DPA) -- German Chancellor Helmut Kohl 
today spoke on the telephone with Russian President Boris 
Yeltsin to gather first-hand information on the formation of the 
government in Moscow, government spokesman Dieter Vogel said in 
Bonn today. [passage omitted] 
