<DOCNO> FBIS3-58914 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drweu016__a94033" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-016 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  25 January 1994 </DATE1>

